{
  "stem": "8916.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I personally never did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would never do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I don't-- I would consider that demeaning, to have to go back there and reclaim that home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I think that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] done.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, it's one of those things that's finished.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would never-- I would never want to possess that home again, or my grandparents' house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, well--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the war began.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And restrictive laws began against the Jews with these-- my-- my father lost his job immediately.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was working in this factory as a tool and die maker and he no longer could work there, because Jews could not work in factories that were non-war-related.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and Jewish ownership was prohibited and businesses were taken away from Jews immediately.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was 1939.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was-- I was going to turn 10 years old that year.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the area was-- where I lived was industrial, in that the glass factory was there and there were several other factories.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, my father used to work at different factories because not every factory had a tool and die maker.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when they had work of that nature, they would ask him to do this for them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a-- do you want to know about my first job?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] There was a factory that made soft drinks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I went there to--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gosh, I don't remember what the name-- I-- I don't know if it had a special name or the bottles were named all these different flavors.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there was citrus or orange flavor, and some other kind of fruit flavor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In any case--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got-- I got a job working in this-- in this factory.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
